What does fraud mean when you stop sick?
After the allowances, the UMP and the government launch the offensive on sick stoppages.
Nicolas Sarkozy will be on Tuesday 15 November in Bordeaux to visit a family allowance fund, and deliver a speech on the theme - recurrent since 2007 - of the fight against social fraud and assistance.
